39:27.999 --> 39:29.899
Erin sleeping
with that guy,

39:29.901 --> 39:32.736
It bothered me,
but it didn't hurt me.

39:32.738 --> 39:34.204
You know what I mean?

39:34.206 --> 39:35.972
No.
Well,
I want to be hurt.

39:35.974 --> 39:37.474
I mean,
I don't want to be hurt,

39:37.476 --> 39:39.042
But I want to feel,
you know,

39:39.044 --> 39:41.644
Or at least feel enough
about a person to be busted up

39:41.646 --> 39:43.880
If they cheat or --
or leave.

39:43.882 --> 39:46.082
Yeah.

39:46.084 --> 39:48.017
I don't want to just
be casual with somebody.

39:48.019 --> 39:50.387
I want to...

39:50.389 --> 39:51.488
Love them.

39:53.692 --> 39:56.159
Somebody's waiting on me.
I got to go. I'll see you later.

39:56.161 --> 39:58.094
Yeah? Hot date?

39:58.096 --> 39:59.562
It's a date.

39:59.564 --> 40:01.931
Who with?

40:01.933 --> 40:04.501
Taxidermy guy from the wedding.
Don't say nothing about it.

40:07.706 --> 40:09.139
[ cellphone rings ]

40:12.210 --> 40:14.844
Hey. Wouldn't peg you
for a facetimer.

40:14.846 --> 40:16.212
[<i> chuckles</i> ]<i> oh, yeah.</i>
<i>Yeah, now here -- here's a tip.</i>

40:16.214 --> 40:18.214
You got to hold that camera
higher,

40:18.216 --> 40:20.016
'cause I'm seeing more than one
of your chins at this angle.

40:20.018 --> 40:21.584
<i> Shut up.</i>

40:21.586 --> 40:23.787
Hey, listen, I hope
it's not too late to call,

40:23.789 --> 40:25.622
But, uh,
I talked with heidi,

40:25.624 --> 40:28.291
<i> And we've discussed it</i>
<i> with the kids, and...</i>

40:28.293 --> 40:29.692
[<i> sighs</i> ]<i> well, I'm in.</i>

40:29.694 --> 40:31.394
Oh, man,
that is great news!

40:31.396 --> 40:33.530
<i> Yeah, but on one condition,</i>
<i> though, all right?</i>

40:33.532 --> 40:35.465
<i> We're all coming,</i>
<i> the entire bell clan.</i>

40:35.467 --> 40:36.599
That's even better.

40:36.601 --> 40:38.601
I'll set plans
in motion right away.

40:38.603 --> 40:41.805
Gonna be a family affair.
Isn't that right, guys?

40:41.807 --> 40:42.772
Hey.
<i> Hey.</i>

40:42.774 --> 40:44.274
<i> We're excited.</i>

40:44.276 --> 40:45.308
<i> All right,</i>
<i> have a good night, luke.</i>

40:45.310 --> 40:46.843
Yeah, okay.
We'll see you.

40:54.486 --> 40:56.319
[ sighs ]

40:59.157 --> 41:01.491
So, tables are wiped down,
I stocked up the glasses,

41:01.493 --> 41:03.726
And I got this bit of empties
to take out to recycle.

41:03.728 --> 41:04.661
Is there anything else?

41:04.663 --> 41:06.496
I think we're good.

41:06.498 --> 41:08.631
Just sit that down
and go on home.

41:08.633 --> 41:10.333
Deacon already split?

41:10.335 --> 41:12.802
Yeah, he's the family man,
not me.

41:12.804 --> 41:15.071
Can you tell him thank you
for me?

41:15.073 --> 41:16.773
And thank you, too,
frankie.

41:16.775 --> 41:18.508
You've earned your keep.

41:18.510 --> 41:19.642
[ chuckles ]

41:19.644 --> 41:20.810
I'll see you tomorrow.

41:20.812 --> 41:22.078
Yeah, I'll see you.

41:24.316 --> 41:26.850
[ chuckles ]

41:26.852 --> 41:28.618
Hey.

41:28.620 --> 41:29.652
Hey.

41:29.654 --> 41:31.488
Did I wake you?
Mnh.

41:31.490 --> 41:34.123
[ both chuckle ]

41:34.125 --> 41:35.291
How'd it go tonight?

41:35.293 --> 41:36.426
It was good. Yeah.

41:36.428 --> 41:37.927
It was the best night
since the opening.

41:37.929 --> 41:39.162
Oh, great.
Yeah.

41:39.164 --> 41:40.163
I tell you
something else, too.

41:40.165 --> 41:42.332
That vita
is a hard worker.

41:42.334 --> 41:43.967
I love it.

41:43.969 --> 41:46.102
I know she's so grateful.

41:46.104 --> 41:49.272
Frankie's not too keen
on the whole thing.
Really?

41:49.274 --> 41:51.641
Well, you know, with
her background and all that,

41:51.643 --> 41:53.142
Guess when
you got a small business,

41:53.144 --> 41:54.677
You got to think
about those things, right?

41:54.679 --> 41:56.513
I think she's
worth the risk, though.

41:56.515 --> 41:57.547
I think so.

41:57.549 --> 41:59.816
She keeps working this hard,
definitely.

41:59.818 --> 42:02.385
[ cellphone rings ]

42:02.387 --> 42:05.488
Well, speak of the devil,
there's frankie now.

42:05.490 --> 42:06.990
Hey, man, what's up?

42:06.992 --> 42:10.326
I hate to say I told you so,
partner, but I told you so.

42:10.328 --> 42:11.694
Hold on, frankie.
What you talking about?

42:11.696 --> 42:14.531
Somebody made off
with $500 from the till tonight.

42:14.533 --> 42:16.466
I think we both know
who took it.

42:16.468 --> 42:18.134
[ sighs ]

42:18.136 --> 42:19.402
Vita.
